'''大青島海戰'''發生於2009年11月10日，為[[朝鮮人民軍海軍|朝鮮人民軍海軍]]與[[大韓民國海軍|大韓民國海軍]]在[[大青島|大青島]]的軍事衝突。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/southkorea/6536557/North-and-South-Korea-warships-exchange-fire.html|title=North and South Korean Ships Exchange Fire|date=2009-10-11|publisher=''[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Telegraph]]''|accessdate=2009-10-11|location=London|first=Peter|last=Foster|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128103621/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/southkorea/6536557/North-and-South-Korea-warships-exchange-fire.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==衝突過程==
11時27分上午左右，一艘[[北韓|北韓]]的海軍巡邏艇越過[[三八線|三八線]]，[[南韓|南韓]]海軍的小船警告三次無效。其中一艘南韓巡邏艇上的士兵鳴槍警告，这直接導致了北韓船艦和南韓船艦的衝突。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://english.yonhapnews.co.kr/national/2009/11/10/27/0301000000AEN20091110007900315F.HTML|title=Koreas clash in Yellow Sea, blame each other|last=Kim|first=Sam|date=November 10, 2009|publisher=[[Yonhap|Yonhap]]|accessdate=2009-11-10|archive-date=2012-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120111154436/http://english.yonhapnews.co.kr/national/2009/11/10/27/0301000000AEN20091110007900315F.HTML|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/nation/2009/11/205_55243.html|title=Seoul Wary of N. Korean Retaliation|date=2009-10-11|publisher=''[[The_Korea_Times|The Korea Times]]''|accessdate=2009-10-11|archive-date=2009-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091113081402/http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/nation/2009/11/205_55243.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[朝鮮中央通訊社|朝鮮中央通訊社]]（即北韓的官方通訊社）聲稱此次事件是由於南韓海軍的挑釁而交鋒，北韓只是在執行海軍的定期警衛任務。11點20分，南韓軍艦對北韓巡邏艇進行追逐並嚴重挑釁，巡邏艇為採取正當防衛而還擊<ref name=kcna>[http://www.kcna.co.jp/item/2009/200911/news10/20091110-08ee.html  DPRK Demands S. Korea Apologize for Armed Provocation] {{Wayback|url=http://www.kcna.co.jp/item/2009/200911/news10/20091110-08ee.html |date=20091215095501 }}. [[Korean_Central_News_Agency|Korean Central News Agency]]. November 10, 2009.</ref>。

==結果==
在爭鬥以後，南韓巡邏艇僅遭受了表面損傷（15個彈孔），沒有傷亡。 而北韓巡邏艇部分被毀壞，雖然沒有從北韓的官方聲明，[[朝鮮中央通訊社|朝鮮中央通訊社]]在南韓報告北韓有四名水兵傷亡的謠言，倖存者則說大約有10位北韓水手在行動喪生，並且要求南韓道歉。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://bemil.chosun.com/nbrd/bbs/view.html?b_bbs_id=10080&pn=1&num=6013 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-07-13 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303165723/http://bemil.chosun.com/nbrd/bbs/view.html?b_bbs_id=10080&pn=1&num=6013 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=kcna/><ref>{{cite news| url = http://news.kukinews.com/article/view.asp?page=1&gCode=kmi&arcid=0001446136&cp=du| title = 《North and South had battle 7 years absence》 South Korea Defense, Reacted immediately following their battle manual… defeated North Korea ship(《남북 7년만에 서해교전》 軍, 눈치 안보고 교전수칙대로 즉각 대응… 北경비정 격퇴)| publisher = ''Kukmin Daily'' (국민일보)| date = 2009-10-11| access-date = 2013-07-13| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110713174259/http://news.kukinews.com/article/view.asp?page=1&gCode=kmi&arcid=0001446136&cp=du| archive-date = 2011-07-13| dead-url = yes}}</ref>。

